  <title translate="true">Top-TIP: Motion-Plan</title>
  <body>
    <para styleclass="" style="text-align:left; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.00; background-color:transparent; white-space:normal; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; border:none; tabstops:none;"><table styleclass="PopupTable" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Tip Body"><text styleclass="Element" translate="true">Top-Tip: </text><text styleclass="Interface" style="font-style:italic;" translate="true">Plan your motion-design for the number of segments.</text></para>
          <list id="0" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI&apos;; font-size:10pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Move all Y-axis motion-values to zero(0), with the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-Blend-Point-Editor" styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Blend-Point</link><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> or </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-Segment-Editor" styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Segment Editor</link><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">.</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Estimate how many segments you need in your motion. </text></li>
            <li styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Use Insert-Blend-Points (or </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-Tools-DeleteSegment" styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Delete-Segments</link><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">) to split the existing segments (or remove segments), to give the total number of segments in your estimate.</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Edit the motion-law, or leave each segment as Flexible-Polynomial.</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Edit the X-axis values of each Blend-Point to approximate values.</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Edit the Y-axis values of the Position graph to the approximate value.</text></li>
            <li styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Continue....</text></li>
          </list>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo" style="margin-left:0px;"></para>
